Tie-Tk-Text
===========

Access Tk text widgets as arrays. Supports Perl/Tk, Tkx, and Tcl::Tk.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

Alternatively, you can use the following commands to install with 
ExtUtils::MakeMaker:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

DEPENDENCIES

None, although you'll need some sort of Perl to Tk bridge for it to be useful.

